items.title: Awesome LaTeX
items.content_text:
### Online editors

*   [Vexlio](https://vexlio.com/) - Online diagram editor with built-in LaTeX equation support including live preview and easy exports.

### Templates / TikZ

*   [TeXtured (⭐183)](https://github.com/jdujava/TeXtured) - A typographically elegant, clean, and structured LaTeX template (primarily intended for theses).
